<ul>
  <li>Edit page number and column to reflect where the rubric starts in the new manuscript,
    <ul>
      <li>This will also effect the ed=‚Äù#V‚Äù, in your line breaks as the letter will need to change to reflect the new manuscript</li>
    </ul>
  </li>
</ul>

<div class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>&lt;div xml:id="starts-on"&gt;
